com.bmc.arsys.qual.antlr.ast

Class ASTQualTreeWalker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.qual.antlr.ast.ARASTTreeWalker
      • com.bmc.arsys.qual.antlr.ast.ASTQualTreeWalker

  • public class ASTQualTreeWalker
extends ARASTTreeWalker
    An extension of the ARASTTreeWalker, that walks through the tree returned from parsing a string, and converts it to a QualifierInfo object.
